 />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3隻眼 8條命 1117被捕 無數斷手斷腳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831黨鐵恐襲傷者消息全無</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><br />\n九二九三大三罷！<br />\n設死線 升級持續罷工<br />\n日日罷工 日日入機場<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【升級罷工】EndGame＝全面開啟升級抗爭</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">網民問卷調查報告 我們在這沉痛的晚上公佈</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1525035\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1525035</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bVP4X9g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbVP4X9g.jpg&h=c7d56cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y5iA4Pi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY5iA4Pi.jpg&h=b866962b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hL7VVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hL7VVY.jpg&h=fc849ad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7bbf8062b86efddb1c5d239c140be810dcb16191","tid":1534041,"uid":272587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:19:54.000Z","msg":"罷緊<br />\n利申紅底浸大"},{"pid":"d4cd16ffcf32ee1a9122051a6282ae0f4746cc48","tid":1534041,"uid":183536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6c5890a81b12165e505ed16ed5871c264801a98","tid":1534041,"uid":157107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T01:32:12.000Z","msg":"唔係話兩個星期架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似個個都返緊學咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係罷嘅我都返架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n罷緊嘅不如留個名 冇人我就返學了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:24:45.000Z","msg":"請大家放上TG,FB,連登,外國媒體，任何Channel，因